  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/gaming/\" rel=\"tag\">游戏产品</a>, <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/industry/\" rel=\"tag\">产业新闻</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/28/nintendo-denies-smartphone-games/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/32782bd1e02662636c116ae2637ec1ad/nint.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n看完之前的<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/28/nintendo-reportedly-planning-mini-games-and-content-for-its-bigg/\">报道</a>，就在大家都以为任天堂终于要在日益崛起的智能手机面前妥协的时候，官方出来辟谣了。搞了半天日经新闻闹了个乌龙，误解了岩田老大的意思。任天堂不久前已经正式向主站编辑确认，称其并没有在智能手机平台上推出「小游戏」的打算，之前社长在财报会议中的发言指的是要利用智能设备来更好地推广任天堂旗下的游戏、角色和硬件。就是嘛，那个顽固的任天堂怎么会说变就变呢...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/01/28/nintendo-denies-smartphone-games/\">Engadget</a></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/28/nintendo-denies-smartphone-games/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20817671/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/28/nintendo-denies-smartphone-games/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
